org.egov.collection.integration.services

Interface CollectionIntegrationService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionIntegrationServiceImpl

    public interface CollectionIntegrationService
    Interface exposed by collections system to other systems (typically billing systems)

    • Method Detail

      • getBillReceiptInfo

        List<BillReceiptInfo> getBillReceiptInfo(String serviceCode,
                                         String refNum)
        Returns the list of bill receipt information objects for given reference number (typically bill number). One bill can be associated with multiple receipts in case of part payments.
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        refNum - The bill reference number
        Returns:
        The bill receipt information

      • getBillReceiptInfo

        Map<String,List<BillReceiptInfo>> getBillReceiptInfo(String serviceCode,
                                                     Set<String> refNums)
        Returns the bill receipt information for given set of reference numbers (typically bill numbers)
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        refNums - Set of bill reference numbers
        Returns:
        Map of bill receipt information objects. Key = bill reference number, value = List of Bill receipt information objects

        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        receiptNum - The Collections or Manual Receipt Number
        Returns:
        The bill receipt information

      • getReceiptInfo

        Map<String,BillReceiptInfo> getReceiptInfo(String serviceCode,
                                           Set<String> receiptNums)
        Returns HashMap of the bill receipt information for given set of receipt numbers
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        receiptNums - Set of Collections or Manual Receipt Number
        Returns:
        Map of bill receipt information objects. Key = bill reference number, value = Bill receipt information object

      • getInstrumentReceiptInfo

        List<BillReceiptInfo> getInstrumentReceiptInfo(String serviceCode,
                                               String instrumentNum)
        Returns set of bill receipt information for given instrument number. One instrument might have been used to pay for more than one bills, hence may belong to more than one receipts.
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        instrumentNum - The instrument number
        Returns:
        The set of bill receipt information objects for given instrument number

      • getInstrumentReceiptInfo

        Map<String,List<BillReceiptInfo>> getInstrumentReceiptInfo(String serviceCode,
                                                           Set<String> instrumentNums)
        Returns the bill receipt information for given set of instrument numbers. Since one instrument may belong to more than one receipts, this method will return a map of instrument number to set of bill receipt information objects.
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        instrumentNums - Set of instrument numbers
        Returns:
        Map of bill receipt information objects. Key = instrument number, value = Set of Bill receipt information objects

      • createReceipt

        BillReceiptInfo createReceipt(BillInfo bill,
                              List<PaymentInfo> paymentInfoList)
        This method creates the receipt for the given bill and payment information
        Parameters:
        bill - an instance of BillInfo containing the bill information.
        paymentInfoList - a List of PaymentInfo containing the payment information. A List is used in order to accommodate payment using multiple cheques/DDs for a single receipt. In all other cases, it should be taken care that only a single mode of payment is permitted, i.e., the List should contain a single entry.
        Returns:
        an instance of BillReceiptInfo containing all details of the created receipt.

      • getOnlinePendingReceipts

        List<BillReceiptInfo> getOnlinePendingReceipts(String serviceCode,
                                               String consumerCode)
        Returns the online pending bill receipt information for given service and consumer code
        Parameters:
        serviceCode - The service code of the billing system
        consumerCode - The consumer code of the billing system
        Returns:
        List of Pending Bill receipt information objects

      • createMiscellaneousReceipt

        BillReceiptInfo createMiscellaneousReceipt(BillInfo bill,
                                           List<PaymentInfo> paymentInfoList)
        This method creates the miscellaneous receipt for the given bill and payment information
        Parameters:
        bill - an instance of BillInfo containing the bill information.
        paymentInfoList - a List of PaymentInfo containing the payment information. A List is used in order to accommodate payment using multiple cheques/DDs for a single receipt. In all other cases, it should be taken care that only a single mode of payment is permitted, i.e., the List should contain a single entry.
        Returns:
        an instance of BillReceiptInfo containing all details of the created receipt.
